title: I'm really trying to decide if or if not, that's a new splash for Zed
body:
I mean at first glance of the icon of course it looks new but then you look at it close and it's posed similar to his current splash

But then you look AGAIN and the eye part of the helmet actually looks a bit different in design and his perspective is slightly moved over a bit....

EDIT : the new icon, not the teaser art
